snippet: Defender Daryl Janmaat’s blunder handed the substitute Vaclav Pilar an injury-time winner as the host Czech Republic beat the Netherlands, 2-1, in the teams’ opening Euro 2016 qualifier.
abstract: Czech Republic beats Netherlands, 2-1, in teams' opening Euro 2016 qualifier; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: Defender Daryl Janmaat’s blunder handed the substitute Vaclav Pilar an injury-time winner as the host Czech Republic beat the Netherlands, 2-1, in the teams’ opening Euro 2016 qualifier.

headline.main: Gaffe Allows Czechs to Defeat Dutch
